<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Atlantic_slave_trade&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Anstey, Roger: <i>The Atlantic Slave Trade and British abolition, 1760-1810</i>. London: Macmillan, 1975.</li>
